                <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-6">AI is transforming healthcare</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">Artificial intelligence is no longer science fiction in healthcare. From clinical decision support and automated administration to predictive analytics &ndash; AI applications are increasingly finding their way into the daily practice of healthcare professionals in the Netherlands.</p>
