                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">By approaching AI not as a standalone technology, but as an integrated component of a broader ecosystem, a scalable and manageable architecture emerges. Healthcare organizations can incrementally activate AI functionality without having to replace their existing systems.</p>
                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">Want to dive deeper into how human-centered AI works in practice? Read our detailed article on <a href="{{ langPrefix }}/insight-mensgerichte-ai-healthcare" class="text-brand-blue hover:text-brand-blue-dark font-medium">human-centered AI in healthcare: from hype to reality</a>.</p>

